    <p style="color: white;">Asriel fight you because he thinks you are Chara his dead sibling, the only one who understood him. He was the first to see Chara after they have fall from above and had adopted Chara as his sibling.</p>
    <p style="color: white;">After Chara and Asriel made a plan to combind their soul and cross the barrier and killing 6 human from the surface. But the plan goes wrong when Asriel came holding Chara's body, the human though he killed them so they kill him. Chara controling half of Asriel tries to attack back and killing everyone but Asriel did not want to and because he was controling half of his body too, they died going back to the underground. thats why Flowey takes the sentence of "KILL OR BE KILLDED!".</p>
